name Wizard
msg
@match hi|hello
Ah,an adventuerer... Have you heard of
the mithril trail?
@match no|No
It is the road connecting to the
Dwarven kingdom of Erthos. It is vary
dangerous with bandits and highwaymen.
But I have heard tell of a secret cave
of a successful bandit. It is said he
knew some of the art of wizardry,and
used his skill to help him in robbing
merchants and travelers. This made him
very successful,but it is said a more
powerful wizard defeated him. And made
the trail safe from his magiks.





endmsg
